Invocation Name: quick earnings announcements
des:
This skill will tell you today's earnings announcements. Simply say: "Alexa, open quick earnings announcements" and Alexa will tell you the ticker symbols for all the companies with earnings announcements today.

Please note: Some days there aren't any earnings announcements. When this happens Alexa will tell you that.
